import { Label } from '@mui/icons-material';
import { Button, Container, Divider, FormControlLabel, FormGroup, List, ListItem, ListItemText, Stack, Switch, TextField } from '@mui/material';
import React, { useState } from 'react';


function CadastroPeixes(){
  const initialValue={
    PitTag:'',
    NC_Especie:'',
    Comp_Padrao:'',
    Local_Captura:'',
    Peso_Soltura:0,
    Local_Soltura:'',
    Cod_Amostra_DNA:'',
    
    

  }
const[value,setValue]=useState(initialValue);

const handleChange=(e)=>{
  const{name,value}=e.target;
  console.log(value);
  setValue({
    ...value,
    [name]:value
  });
  console.log(value);
};

 return (
    <Container maxWidth="sm" >
    <div >
      <List>
        <ListItem >
          <ListItemText primary="Dados de cadastro dos peixes" />
        </ListItem>
        <Divider />
      </List>
      <Stack spacing={2} direction='row'  >
        <Stack direction='column' spacing={2}   >

          <TextField
            name='PitTag'
            label="PitTag"
            variant='outlined'
            color='primary'
            required
            value={value.PitTag}
            onChange={handleChange}

          />

          <TextField
            name='Comp_Padrao'
            label="Comprimento Padrão"
            variant='outlined'
            color='primary'
            required
            value={value.Comp_Padrao}
            onChange={handleChange}
          />


          <TextField

            label="Local de Captura"
            variant='outlined'
            color='primary'
            required
          />
          <TextField

            label="Data de Soltura"
            variant='outlined'
            color='primary'
            required />
          <TextField

            label="Código da Amostra de DNA"
            variant='outlined'
            color='primary'
            required />
        </Stack>

        <Stack direction='column' spacing={2}   >

          <TextField

            label="Nome Científico da Espécie"
            variant='outlined'
            color='primary'
            required

          />
          <TextField

            label="Comprimento total"
            variant='outlined'
            color='primary'
            required

          />
          <TextField

            label="Peso na Soltura"
            variant='outlined'
            color='primary'
            required

          />
          <TextField

            label="Local da soltura"
            variant='outlined'
            color='primary'
            required

          />
          <FormGroup>
            <FormControlLabel label="Recaptura" control={<Switch defaultChecked />} />

          </FormGroup>
        </Stack>
      </Stack>
    </div >

    <div>
    <List>
      <ListItem >
        <ListItemText primary="Informações de Recaptura" />
      </ListItem>
      <Divider />
    </List>
    <Stack spacing={2} direction='row'   >
      <Stack direction='column' spacing={2}   >
       
        <TextField

          label="Comprimento total"
          variant='outlined'
          color='primary'
          required

        />

        <TextField

          label="Peso na soltura"
          variant='outlined'
          color='primary'
          required
        />


        <TextField

          label="Local da Soltura"
          variant='outlined'
          color='primary'
          required
        />
        <TextField

          label="Recaptura"
          variant='outlined'
          color='primary'
          required />

      </Stack>

      <Stack direction='column' spacing={2}   >

        <TextField

          label="Local da Captura"
          variant='outlined'
          color='primary'
          required

        />
        <TextField

          label="Data de Captura"
          variant='outlined'
          color='primary'
          required

        />
        <TextField

          label="Código da Amostra de DNA"
          variant='outlined'
          color='primary'
          required

        />

        <Button size='small' variant='outlined' color='inherit' >Salvar</Button>
        
      </Stack>
    </Stack>
  </div >
</Container >
 );   
}
export default CadastroPeixes;
